== [[Indonesian]] ==

# [[no]]
# [[not]]

===[[synonyms]]===

# [[tak]]
# [[tiada]]


'''Tidak''' is used to negate verbs and adjectives. For negating nouns the word [[bukan]] must be used. 

===examples===

# [[Saya]] '''tidak''' [[mau]] [[makan]].
#* [[I]] don't [[want]] [[to]] [[eat]].

# [[Buku]] [[itu]] '''tidak''' [[mahal]].
#* [[That]] [[book]] is [[not]] [[expensive]].

# [[Ini]] '''bukan''' [[buku]] [[saya]].
#* [[This]] is [[not]] [[my]] [[book]].